In the INTEREST OF M.M. and I.M., Minor Children, C.J., Mother, Petitioner-Appellee, G.M., Father, Respondent-Appellant. No. 18-0728 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 5, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

A father appeals the termination of his parental rights to two sons under Iowa Code chapter 600A. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
